&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;Tomorrow morning, I&amp;rsquo;ll begin grading your Introduction  activity  which, as the syllabus states, is a component of your  participation  grade in the class. You&amp;rsquo;ll receive a letter grade for the  activity. When  I evaluate your work, I&amp;rsquo;ll basically be looking to see  how well you  followed directions. For instance, if your post does not  meet length  expectations, your grade will reflect that. Once I&amp;rsquo;ve  posted grades,  I&amp;rsquo;ll let everyone know&amp;mdash;this way, you won&amp;rsquo;t have to keep  checking the  gradebook to see if grades have been posted yet.&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
